com.yworks.yfiles.geometry

Class InsetsD

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.geometry.InsetsD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IStruct, Cloneable

    public final class InsetsD
extends Object
implements com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IStruct
    An immutable struct that models the thickness of insets as double precision floating point values.
